                        of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS2377Bakaffa">Bakāffā</persName>, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5617IyasuII">Iyāsu II</persName>
                        (also <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5618IyasuII">III</persName> and <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5619IyasuIV">IV</persName>),
                        <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5636IyoasI">ʾIyoʾās I</persName> (and <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5637IyoasI">II</persName>), <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9153TaklaHa">Takla Haymānot II</persName>, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8421Salomon">Salomon</persName>,
                      <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9142TaklaGi">Takla Giyorgis</persName>, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5332hezqeyas">Ḥǝzqǝyās</persName>, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10441Yonas">Yonās</persName>,
                      <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3501Demetros">Dǝmeṭros</persName>, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3692egwalas">ʾƎgʷāla Ṣǝyon or Gʷālu</persName>,
                      <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4661Gigar">Gigār</persName>, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4264GabraKr">Gabra Krǝstos</persName> and <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8344sahlaDe">Sāhlu</persName>. The following
                    are the most important of them.</note>
                  </item>

                          <item xml:id="a2">
                            <locus target="#215r"/>
                            <desc type="LandGrant">Deed of gift by <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS2377Bakaffa">Bakāffā</persName> to the priests of the church of Raphael.</desc>
                            <q xml:lang="gez">ነዋ፡ ወሀብነ፡ ንሕነ፡ ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡ በካፋ። ለካህናት፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ሩፋኤል፡ ከመ፡ ይኩነነ፡ ለመድኃኒተ፡ ሥጋ፡ ወነፍስ። ፬፻፵፯ምድር፡
